data.description: Welcome to your charming lakefront home, where rustic northern aesthetics blend harmoniously with warm Florida weather! This enchanting residence features 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, with 3 of the bedrooms overlooking a luscious bamboo garden oasis and a private lake view. The owner's suite is located on the second floor and boasts an extended walk-on balcony showcasing a beautifully positioned view over the lake. Step inside, and you'll be greeted by a bonus den space, a formal dining room (currently used as gameroom), and an inviting kitchen wrapped in elegant granite countertops with bar seating. The wood-burning fireplace adds a touch of coziness, while the cedar panel ceilings evoke a sense of natural allure. Upstairs, bamboo flooring complements the serene ambiance. Situated on a wooded and private lot spanning over a third of an acre, this home offers shaded tranquility, courtesy of mature trees, including the rare and distinctive black bamboo. The new 2023 metal roof ensures durability and charm, while the two 2.5-ton AC units (2014 and 2020) maintain a pleasantly cooled living space of nearly 2,500 sqft. Additionally, the 2022 water softener system adds to the convenience of quality water without the utility bill. Located just minutes away from parks, neighbrohood dining, and the desirable Fort Pierce Inlet, this residence strikes the perfect balance between seclusion and accessibility. With no intrusive HOA restrictions and an extended driveway; you're free to bring your boats, RVs, and more, making it an ideal destination for leisure and exploration. Beyond the allure of the interior, this home beckons you outdoors to enjoy the breathtaking private lake view, perfect for recreational fishing and tranquil moments. The backyard features a screened patio and a lovely brick paver path, creating a beautiful space for gardening, BBQs, and cherished family and friend get-togethers. As you immerse yourself in the ambiance of this lakeside retreat, you'll find a sanctuary of warmth and beauty, inviting you to create memories that will last a lifetime. Welcome to a timeless haven where nature and elegance converge to embrace you with open arms. (room sizes approx)
